<section class="advanced-demo dream-demo" aria-label="现场光、高光溢出和梦境感示意图">
  <div class="advanced-demo__grid">
    <div class="advanced-demo__card">
      <div class="advanced-demo__badge">现场光源</div>
      <div class="advanced-demo__scene dream-demo__scene dream-demo__scene--light">
        <div class="dream-demo__lamp">灯</div>
        <div class="dream-demo__glow"></div>
        <div class="dream-demo__face">脸</div>
      </div>
      <p>现场光源不一定要干净。路灯、便利店、车灯、屏幕光都能制造不真实感，重点是让光有方向和层次。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advanced-demo__card">
      <div class="advanced-demo__badge">高光溢出</div>
      <div class="advanced-demo__scene dream-demo__scene dream-demo__scene--bloom">
        <div class="dream-demo__white">溢出</div>
        <div class="dream-demo__float">漂浮</div>
        <div class="dream-demo__memory">模糊记忆</div>
      </div>
      <p>高光溢出可以让画面像梦、像回忆、像不稳定的片段。但要主动保留暗部锚点，画面才不会全散掉。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
